  "texts": [
    "This patchwork of rules underscores a need for greater international coordination, which we address later in our recommendations and future directions.",
    "Despite new regulations, significant challenges remain in addressing AI-fueled disinformation.",
    "One major issue is global fragmentation of AI governance.",
    "The lack of uniform rules across jurisdictions creates opportunities for malicious actors to engage in regulatory arbitrage -exploiting gaps by operating from countries with lax or no AI oversight.",
    "For example, an organization banned from deploying certain AI-generated content in the EU could base its operations in a country with weaker laws and still target EU audiences online."
